  "texts": [
    "The plates were then transferred to a 37 °C incubator with 5% CO2 and 95% humidity.",
    "Tumor cells were seeded onto OBSCs 2 h after slicing, with one tumor seeded in the center of each hemisphere for a total of two tumor foci per OBSC.",
    "BSM was changed 24 h after slicing.",
    "Fluorescence images were taken 24 h postseeding for normalization of tumor size.",
    "Bioluminescence readouts were taken at 96 h post seeding for assessment of cell viability."
